Americans and
local Kurdish fighters called
the Peshmerga.

27:51.904 --> 27:57.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They named themselves the
Nineveh Plains Forces,
after this area north of Mosul
where many

27:57.776 --> 28:04.116 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Christian villages were
attacked. With less
than 300 men fighting, their
presence here

28:04.149 --> 28:09.922 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
