believes they can help their
people.

28:09.955 --> 28:14.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAFAA KHAMRO, Nineveh Plains
Forces (through
translator): Now we have only
one unit. We

28:14.126 --> 28:19.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
