28:53.966 --> 28:57.102 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And how does it feel to have
ISIS living in
your house?

28:57.135 --> 29:06.278 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GEORGE, Nineveh Plains Forces:
It's a bad
feeling, so aggravated, so
angry, so mad.

29:06.311 --> 29:13.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, since they started here and
created this
force, I hear about it, and I
came and volunteered

29:13.719 --> 29:23.829 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
