did to us.

29:27.799 --> 29:32.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: He thinks there
is too much
bad blood here for things to be
the same again.

29:32.971 --> 29:39.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If Da'esh, or ISIS, are defeated
and they
are pushed out of Mosul, is it
going to be

29:39.077 --> 29:43.115 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
