communities here to
live side by side with their
neighbors?

29:43.148 --> 29:46.985 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GEORGE: Yes, I think it's going
to be hard
and difficult.

29:47.019 --> 29:51.056 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: George blames his
Muslim neighbors
for not standing up to ISIS.

29:51.089 --> 30:01.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GEORGE: They saw a lot of, like,
bad things,
