communicate with
them again.

30:07.973 --> 30:14.579 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: The men practice
house searches
amongst the remnants of the very
communities

30:14.613 --> 30:16.915 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
